    {
        "url": "/quotes/arne_glimcher_558103",
        "quote": "In the early 1990s we witnessed the emergence of a revitalized contemporary Chinese art world that began as a reaction against the government-approved Social Realist style. Zhang Xiaogang, Huang Yong Ping, Ai WeiWei, Yue Minjun, and Wang Guangyi were among the first group of artists to establish a movement that became known as Cynical Realism.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Arne Glimcher",
            "url": "/quotes/arne_glimcher_558103"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Against",
